<subSubSection pageId="43" pageNumber="527" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="43.[103,1314,1193,2767]" pageId="43" pageNumber="527">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[107,456,2579,2608]" pageId="43" pageNumber="527">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List (as 
<taxonomicName class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Lonchophylla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="527" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="cadenai">Lonchophylla cadenai</taxonomicName>
). Available information is inadequate to make reliable assessments of conservation risks to Cadena’s Nectar Bat.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
